/Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A1n/poem-Xc4evkfuvb_JLemMkjJVAw">Nguyên đán - 元旦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-T%C3%ADnh-Phu/author-5VBdkDLCcLTpFT7k3ZzmYg">Ngải Tính Phu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Phong-Ph%E1%BA%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%8B-v%C5%A9/poem--R9peCRbIkzM2rwcKRMRZw">Phong Phạn tự tị vũ - 封飯寺避雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Quan-L%C3%BD-C%E1%BB%91-Th%E1%BB%89nh-t%C6%B0-m%C3%A3-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-CI17vANvnGuZPBg85EtKIg">Quan Lý Cố Thỉnh tư mã đệ sơn thuỷ đồ kỳ 3 - 觀李固請司馬弟山水圖其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/%C6%AFu-l%C3%A3o/poem-qIyjHbe0mdIhfT_8koDJGA">Ưu lão - 憂老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
